Every once in a while,

00:08:43.280 --> 00:08:46.570
someone will send me a
quite earnest question

00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:49.170
about something they saw on the internet.

00:08:49.170 --> 00:08:52.860
And one of the things I've
heard about quite a bit

00:08:52.860 --> 00:08:54.660
in the last couple of
weeks as we've been talking

00:08:54.660 --> 00:08:59.160
about hormones and food
intake and how those interact

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:02.670
is this question of are certain foods

00:09:02.670 --> 00:09:06.680
particularly good for
certain organs of the body?

00:09:06.680 --> 00:09:08.930
And can that be predicted

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:12.180
on the basis of the shape of those foods?

00:09:12.180 --> 00:09:14.860
So first of all, I want to
acknowledge the question

00:09:14.860 --> 00:09:17.360
as a valid one, because I see this

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:18.630
every once in a while out there.

00:09:18.630 --> 00:09:19.840
People will say, well, you know,

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:21.770
walnuts are in the shape of the brain

00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:25.430
and therefore they are good
for your brain or, you know,

00:09:25.430 --> 00:09:29.150
a particular fruit like the
beet often looks like a heart

00:09:29.150 --> 00:09:30.890
and it's good for your heart.

00:09:30.890 --> 00:09:34.440
And I certainly invite
questions of all kinds,

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:36.210
provided they're sincere questions.

00:09:36.210 --> 00:09:41.210
However, I am not aware
of any science whatsoever

00:09:41.250 --> 00:09:44.830
supporting the idea that
the shape of a given food

00:09:44.830 --> 00:09:48.730
or object for that matter is relevant

00:09:48.730 --> 00:09:52.520
to its functional role in the
body in reference to biology.

00:09:52.520 --> 00:09:54.670
Now, beets contain something

00:09:54.670 --> 00:09:55.710
that we're going to talk about today.

00:09:55.710 --> 00:09:58.410
They contain a substance called arginine,

00:09:58.410 --> 00:10:00.810
which actually can control the dilation

00:10:00.810 --> 00:10:02.800
of blood vessels and arteries.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:05.763
So it has some relationship
to heart and heart health.

00:10:06.610 --> 00:10:09.400
Walnuts contain various fatty acids

00:10:09.400 --> 00:10:12.220
that maybe, I want to underscore maybe,

00:10:12.220 --> 00:10:15.230
beneficial for certain
aspects of brain health

00:10:15.230 --> 00:10:18.010
but there's no evidence whatsoever

00:10:18.010 --> 00:10:20.970
that the shape of the
food itself is relevant.

00:10:20.970 --> 00:10:22.760
And, you know, I think what's happened is,

00:10:22.760 --> 00:10:24.930
is that people have gone out there

00:10:24.930 --> 00:10:27.370
and found foods that
contain certain substances

00:10:27.370 --> 00:10:29.130
like carrots and vitamin A

00:10:29.130 --> 00:10:31.530
or walnuts and particular fatty acids

00:10:31.530 --> 00:10:33.960
or beets and arginine.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:36.080
And they've selected the foods

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:38.410
that happen to be in
the shape of the thing,

00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:42.300
the organ that the particular
substance like vitamin A

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:46.580
or fatty acids and so forth
might benefit or support.

00:10:46.580 --> 00:10:49.370
But of course, there are
many, many other sources

00:10:49.370 --> 00:10:53.620
of these nutrients that
don't come from walnuts

00:10:53.620 --> 00:10:56.110
or from beets or from carrots.

00:10:56.110 --> 00:10:58.660
And so I guess the short way to put it

00:10:58.660 --> 00:11:02.390
is that the idea that
the shape of some food

00:11:02.390 --> 00:11:05.010
is an indication of
whether or not that food

00:11:05.010 --> 00:11:07.010
would be healthy for a
particular organ in the body

00:11:07.010 --> 00:11:09.640
is absolutely unfounded.

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:11.620
I don't know of any evidence for it

00:11:11.620 --> 00:11:15.170
and I'm not out to quash
anybody's great love

00:11:15.170 --> 00:11:16.003
of these foods.

00:11:16.003 --> 00:11:18.030
I enjoy all the foods I just described,

00:11:18.030 --> 00:11:21.520
but the shape of things
in the physical universe

00:11:21.520 --> 00:11:25.650
bears very little, if any, relevance

00:11:25.650 --> 00:11:28.690
to the nutrients that it contains

00:11:28.690 --> 00:11:31.560
and therefore the organs that it supports.

00:11:31.560 --> 00:11:33.400
