Several times before on this podcast,

00:58:23.600 --> 00:58:25.940
I've talked about the fact
that I'm not a big fan

00:58:25.940 --> 00:58:30.240
of melatonin supplementation
for most purposes.

00:58:30.240 --> 00:58:33.393
It might be helpful under
conditions of jet lag.

