You must clear this with your doctor.

01:29:45.650 --> 01:29:47.500
Now, what happens in high heat?

01:29:47.500 --> 01:29:48.780
A couple things happen in high heat.

01:29:48.780 --> 01:29:50.050
First of all,

01:29:50.050 --> 01:29:52.410
you start getting bigger
stroke volume of the heart.

01:29:52.410 --> 01:29:53.550
Kind of like an exercise.

01:29:53.550 --> 01:29:55.730
Once you get well-trained
in endurance activity,

01:29:55.730 --> 01:29:57.220
your stroke volume and the amount of blood

01:29:57.220 --> 01:29:59.663
that your heart can pump
each time gets larger.

01:30:00.750 --> 01:30:02.890
You dilate the blood vessels, right?

01:30:02.890 --> 01:30:04.040
There are a lot of
things that happen also.

01:30:04.040 --> 01:30:04.873
You're sweating.

01:30:04.873 --> 01:30:06.693
Your body's trying to unload heat.

01:30:08.140 --> 01:30:11.460
Dilation of blood vessels,
arginine, increases in heat.

01:30:11.460 --> 01:30:14.670
We're starting to see
and hear a common theme.

01:30:14.670 --> 01:30:17.200
But it appears that getting into,

01:30:17.200 --> 01:30:18.360
I'm not saying getting the body

01:30:18.360 --> 01:30:20.847
up to 212 degrees Fahrenheit,
I want to be very clear,

01:30:20.847 --> 01:30:22.480
I'm not talking about getting the body

01:30:22.480 --> 01:30:23.930
up to 100 degrees Celsius.

01:30:23.930 --> 01:30:25.510
That would be terrible.

01:30:25.510 --> 01:30:26.450
You would die.

01:30:26.450 --> 01:30:30.210
But entering environments
where it's very hot

01:30:30.210 --> 01:30:31.410
for short periods of time,

01:30:31.410 --> 01:30:34.203
anywhere from 20 minutes to 30 minutes,

01:30:35.980 --> 01:30:39.020
where the temperature
is 80 degrees Celsius

01:30:39.020 --> 01:30:42.570
to 100 degrees Celsius or
175 degrees Fahrenheit,

01:30:42.570 --> 01:30:45.260
more or less, to about
210 degrees Fahrenheit,

01:30:45.260 --> 01:30:48.920
more or less, has been shown to increase

01:30:48.920 --> 01:30:51.770
growth hormone release 16 fold.

01:30:51.770 --> 01:30:53.200
That's right, 16 fold.

01:30:53.200 --> 01:30:55.830
That's 1,600%.

01:30:55.830 --> 01:30:58.060
Now, there are also
effects on other hormones,

01:30:58.060 --> 01:31:00.540
prolactin, cortisol, et cetera.

01:31:00.540 --> 01:31:04.030
So the pattern that was
described in this study

01:31:04.030 --> 01:31:05.780
and there've been many studies now.

01:31:06.890 --> 01:31:11.890
Endocrine effects of repeated
sauna were done in 17 humans.

01:31:14.320 --> 01:31:16.530
This was from doing this repeatedly.

01:31:16.530 --> 01:31:17.900
So it wasn't the first time they did this.

01:31:17.900 --> 01:31:19.940
They had to do this three days in a row.

01:31:19.940 --> 01:31:23.310
And the pattern was to get
into the sauna for 20 minutes,

01:31:23.310 --> 01:31:25.470
followed by a 30-minute cooling period.

01:31:25.470 --> 01:31:26.440
Remember, you don't want to spend

01:31:26.440 --> 01:31:27.770
long periods of time at high heat.

01:31:27.770 --> 01:31:30.910
You can cook your brain and other tissues.

01:31:30.910 --> 01:31:33.370
Be very careful as you
approach this if you decide to.

01:31:33.370 --> 01:31:36.590
But 30 minutes, excuse
me, 20 minutes sauna,

01:31:36.590 --> 01:31:38.160
followed by 30 minutes of cooling,

01:31:38.160 --> 01:31:40.650
followed by 20 minutes sauna again,

01:31:40.650 --> 01:31:42.720
led to a five fold
increase in growth hormone.

01:31:42.720 --> 01:31:47.160
And then by doing that
day after day after day,

01:31:47.160 --> 01:31:50.170
on the third day, you would
see these huge increases

01:31:50.170 --> 01:31:52.680
of like 16 fold, up to 16 fold.

01:31:52.680 --> 01:31:54.470
And there are now many studies like this.

01:31:54.470 --> 01:31:59.470
This was described a few
years ago, but since then,

01:32:01.500 --> 01:32:03.210
there've been a number of
other studies that have pointed

01:32:03.210 --> 01:32:07.920
in the direction of
deliberate hyperthermia,

01:32:07.920 --> 01:32:10.000
but not too hot that you kill yourself

01:32:10.000 --> 01:32:11.950
in order to increase growth hormone.

01:32:11.950 --> 01:32:13.790
And I know I keep highlighting
