01:33:40.280 --> 01:33:43.920
are increased activity of
neurons within the hypothalamus

01:33:43.920 --> 01:33:46.860
that stimulate growth hormone
release from the pituitary.

01:33:46.860 --> 01:33:48.160
And that's probably

01:33:48.160 --> 01:33:51.700
because the growth
hormone-releasing hormone neurons

01:33:51.700 --> 01:33:54.470
