01:35:07.080 --> 01:35:08.770
early in the day when you wake up.

01:35:08.770 --> 01:35:13.350
But sauna definitely led to
significant decrease in cortisol

01:35:13.350 --> 01:35:17.540
but did not change testosterone,
DHEA or prolactin levels.

