life and so they're doing that

01:39:58.640 --> 01:39:59.473
because they believe

01:39:59.473 --> 01:40:01.750
it's the right thing
for them, prescription.

01:40:01.750 --> 01:40:03.110
Sermorelin is prescription.

01:40:03.110 --> 01:40:03.990
Do they work?

01:40:03.990 --> 01:40:05.520
Yes.

01:40:05.520 --> 01:40:08.030
Do they shut down your natural production

01:40:08.030 --> 01:40:10.770
of growth hormone-releasing hormone?

01:40:10.770 --> 01:40:13.340
Well, there, the answer is yes

01:40:13.340 --> 01:40:16.400
but some of these peptides
actually have the effect

01:40:16.400 --> 01:40:18.410
of changing gene expression.

01:40:18.410 --> 01:40:19.690
Remember, way back to the beginning

01:40:19.690 --> 01:40:21.020
when I was talking about hormones,

01:40:21.020 --> 01:40:22.760
they can actually change gene expression

01:40:22.760 --> 01:40:25.630
and they can actually
set pathways in motion

01:40:25.630 --> 01:40:27.580
for continued production of a hormone

01:40:27.580 --> 01:40:29.920
even if you stop taking the compound.

